# ─── scrcpy-server binary ────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# The embedded scrcpy-server.jar (~716 KB) is obtained via:
#   make fetch-deps          # downloads from GitHub releases automatically
#
# You have two options:
#   A) Commit the file (simplest for a private repo – uncomment the line below to un-ignore):
#      git add -f internal/stream/scrcpy-server.jar
#
#   B) Keep it out of git and rely on `make fetch-deps` / CI (current default):
internal/stream/scrcpy-server.jar
